Software for Little Magic Boxes (stay tuned).

A Node.js application http://github.com/ry/node for Linux

Requires socket.io in elembe directory http://github.com/LearnBoost/Socket.IO

Requires these node modules:
  node-inotify http://github.com/c4milo/node-inotify
  node-sqlite http://github.com/networkimprov/node-sqlite
  uuidjs http://github.com/weaver/uuidjs
  gm http://github.com/aheckmann/gm
  socket.io-node http://github.com/LearnBoost/Socket.IO-node

Requires these libraries:
  SQLite
  libuuid
  Graphicsmagick

Requires Samba file server http://samba.org/
  configure a share called sqltest on elembe/sqltest/

Requires Firefox browser http://mozilla.org/

Requires AppLaunch Firefox extension https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/240637/

Start with
  $ node elembe.js
Point Firefox to http://yourhost:8000/

